# Issue and Fix (orchestrator)

When the user says **/issue-and-fix**, **issue and fix**, **revisar y arreglar**, **agent review local**, or Agent Review failed with **insufficient funds**:

## Load orchestrator skill

Read and follow: `.cursor/skills/issue-and-fix/SKILL.md`

## Default pipeline (`full`)

1. **Bugbot** (readonly subagent) — findings table
2. **bmc-issue-fix-reviewer** — apply fixes (parent executes skill, not readonly)
3. **Security** (readonly) — only if auth/secrets/server config touched
4. **expert-debug-autonomous** — only if lint/test still failing
5. **`npm run gate:local`**

## Modes

- `full` (default), `fix-only`, `review-only`, `security`

## Related

- Fix skill: `.cursor/skills/bmc-issue-fix-reviewer/SKILL.md`
- Agent: `.cursor/agents/bmc-issue-fix-reviewer.md`
